OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776082266
OL,3,CRory McIlroy looks for answers on the
OL,4,Crange as Masters lead vanishes
OL,6,FWhile all of his rivals were going
OL,7,Funder par ` the nine players
OL,8,Fimmediately below him all shot sub-70
OL,9,Frounds ` the world number two could
OL,10,Frecord only a one-over 71 having come
OL,11,Funstuck at Amen Corner.
OL,13,FThe troubles off the tee which he has
OL,14,Fbeen successfully managing all week
OL,15,Fcost him dearly and he immediately
OL,16,Fretired to the range to find a fix
OL,17,Fahead of his final-group pairing with
OL,18,FCameron Young, who shot a Masters-best
OL,19,F65, on 11 under.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
