PN,44903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776082266
OL,3,CRory McIlroy looks for answers on the
OL,4,Crange as Masters lead vanishes
OL,6,F"The course was obviously gettable,
OL,7,Fthere was a lot of good scores out
OL,8,Fthere, and the quality of the chasing
OL,9,Fpack is obvious," said McIlroy.
OL,11,F"There's a lot of guys in with a
OL,12,Fchance tomorrow. I'm still tied for
OL,13,Fthe best score going into tomorrow, so
OL,14,FI can't forget that, but I do know I'm
OL,15,Fgoing to have to be better if I want
OL,16,Fto have a chance to win.
OL,18,F"I'm in the final group. I just need
OL,19,Fto go to the range and try to figure
OL,20,Fit out a little bit."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@QO]sD@AOUzD@AOU|D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/6
