OL,3,CRory McIlroy looks for answers on the
OL,4,Crange as Masters lead vanishes
OL,6,FMcIlroy entered Augusta National's
OL,7,Ffamously tricky Amen Corner stretch at
OL,8,F13 under, three ahead but clinging on.
OL,10,FHe exited it one behind Young after
OL,11,Fplaying it double bogey-bogey-par
OL,12,Fhaving pulled a seven iron into the
OL,13,Fwater at the 11th, missing the green
OL,14,Fat the next and driving into the trees
OL,15,Fat the 13th.
OL,17,F"When you're not quite feeling it, you
OL,18,Fstruggle. You have to dig deep and I
OL,19,Ffelt like I did that on the front nine
OL,20,Fand made a lot of good par saves," he
OL,21,Fadded.
OL,26,@yD@AOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/6
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
