CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F449A1776082266
OL,3,CRory McIlroy looks for answers on the
OL,4,Crange as Masters lead vanishes
OL,6,F"I missed a couple of chances on eight
OL,7,Fand nine and then I thought I turned
OL,8,Fthe round around with the birdie on 10.
OL,10,F"I felt like I hit a pretty good
OL,11,Fsecond shot on 11 but it just drifted
OL,12,Fon the wind a little bit and went in
OL,13,Fthe water. Those two holes (11 and 12)
OL,14,Fweren't great.
OL,16,F"But again I felt like I bounced back
OL,17,Fpretty well with the birdies on 14 and
OL,18,F15. It would have been nice to play
OL,19,Fthose last few holes and not make that
OL,20,Fbogey on 17 but, you know, I still
OL,21,Fhave a great chance."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUxD@AOU}D@UO]
